When Suzanne Shaw married Peter Cook on the back of his tumultuous divorce with supermodel Christie Brinkley, she chose to ignore the warnings.

But in a complete reversal, Shaw has now written to Brinkley to personally apologize for not heeding her cautions about Cook's philandering.

Cook's marriage to Brinkley collapsed in a very bitter and public divorce trial in 2008 following revelations he had an affair with his 18-year-old assistant Diana Bianchi.

While Bianchi, now 29, has since gone on to marry a New York writer, Shaw has divorced from Cook and written a letter to Brinkley to try and mend their rift.

